author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of J Roddy Walston and the Business, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2013.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Hard Times
00:03:17 Marigold
00:06:13 Heavy Bells

Musicians
J Roddy Walston — vocals, guitar, piano
Steve Colmus — drums
Billy Gordon — guitar
Logan Davis — bass

Credits
Engineer – Mike DeMark
Producer – Jade
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
